---
title: Chipotle-Glazed BBQ Pork with Sour Cream, Garlic Cauli-Broccoli Rice & Charred Corn Salsa
description: Give pork loin a dash of flair with a glaze of chipotle sauce and tangy barbecue seasoning for a melding of robust flavours. Then, ramp up your dish with a wholesome serving of garlicky cauli-broccoli rice. This one’s an exciting ride from start to finish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
